 options in Salento.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5.jpg\" alt=\"salento cocora valley colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"229\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salento cocora valley colombia\" class=\"wp-image-81797 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1299px) 100vw, 1299px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5.jpg 1299w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-406x600.jpg 406w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-548x810.jpg 548w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-229x338.jpg 229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-110x163.jpg 110w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-122x180.jpg 122w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-520x768.jpg 520w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-693x1024.jpg 693w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-731x1080.jpg 731w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-974x1440.jpg 974w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-300x443.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-600x887.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-150x222.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09134439\/salento-colombia-5.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/cocora-valley\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cocora Valley<\/a> Tour<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Jump in a Willy (the original Jeep, which is about 60 years old!) at the town square before 9 AM so you can arrive before the crowds. Once you arrive, you&#x2019;ll be met with a landscape that looks straight from a painting; towering palm trees emerge out of the low-lying clouds as the sun&#x2019;s rays pass through them. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131237\/SA72277.jpg\" alt=\"things to do salento colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"259\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do salento colombia\" class=\"wp-image-81781 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1469px) 100vw, 1469px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131237\/SA72277.jpg 1469w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131237\/SA72277-459x600.jpg 459w, https:\/\/static.