ut a 5-6 hour hike. It&#x2019;s well worth the effort, though, as you pass through cloud forests, jungle, and wax trees. This is the best thing to do in Salento!<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"181196P20,59388P56,260268P1\" data-vi-campaign=\"salento-colombia-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            \n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24.jpg\" alt=\"salento things to do cocora valley hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"262\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salento things to do cocora valley hike\" class=\"wp-image-81886 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1491px) 100vw, 1491px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24.jpg 1491w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24-466x600.jpg 466w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24-629x810.jpg 629w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24-262x338.jpg 262w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24-127x163.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24-140x180.jpg 140w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colombia-24-596x768.jpg 596w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134838\/salento-colomb