r\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10122628\/salento-colombia-17.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-3-mirador-de-salento\">3. Mirador de Salento<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enjoy the best views of Salento and the surrounding countryside at the Mirador de Salento (viewpoint). It&#x2019;s a steep staircase, but walk only 5 minutes up, and you&#x2019;ll be rewarded with stunning views over the small town, the green mountains, and the luscious nature. Visiting at sunset is even more spectacular, although this is also the busiest time.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best of all, the Mirador de Salento is free to visit!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/salento-hotels\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Salento.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10122601\/salento-colombia-14.jpg\" alt=\"Mirador de Salento\"><\/noscript><img width=\"259\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Mirador de Salento\" class=\"wp-image-81851 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1473px) 100vw, 1473px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10122601\/salento-colombia-14.jpg 1473w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202