                  <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> at the weekends, the local market is held in Plaza de Bolivar. It&#x2019;s a great time to shop for some local handicrafts and watch the older men with their traditional sombreros and ponchos playing music and chatting with each other.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8.jpg\" alt=\"salento Plaza de Bolivar\"><\/noscript><img width=\"264\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salento Plaza de Bolivar\" class=\"wp-image-81867 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1499px) 100vw, 1499px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8.jpg 1499w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8-468x600.jpg 468w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8-632x810.jpg 632w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8-264x338.jpg 264w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8-127x163.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8-141x180.jpg 141w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10125819\/salento-colombia-8-600x769.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022