ing tour in Salento<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27.jpg\" alt=\"salento bird watching\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salento bird watching\" class=\"wp-image-81907 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-600x776.