ther from your hostel, drink a beer, and enjoy a bit of competition with one of the top things to do in Salento. There are a few places you can go and play, and it should only cost under 10000 COP for a round of Tejo. Los Amigos is one of the most popular places to play in the area (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/place\/Cancha+De+Tejo+Los+Amigos\/@4.6396151,-75.5694988,15z\/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0xa775762def0bb28f?sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjK89qXxcP3AhVOQMAKHSckAx4Q_BJ6BAhSEAU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here is the location<\/a>).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/salento-hotels\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Salento.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12.jpg\" alt=\"Tejo colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"429\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Tejo colombia\" class=\"wp-image-81839 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-762x600.jpg 762w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-1029x810.jpg 1029w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-429x338.jpg 429w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-163x128.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-229x180.jpg 229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-768x605.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-1024x806.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-1371x1080.jpg 1371w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-1829x1440.jpg 1829w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-300x236.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-600x473.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-150x118.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12-30x24.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100556\/salento-colombia-12.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-8-horseback-riding\">8. Horseback Riding<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Horseback riding in Salento is a bucket list experience, particularly amongst the wax trees of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/cocora-valley\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cocora Valley<\/a>. You&#x2019;ll get to see the beautiful landscape from a new perspective and learn so much more about the area from knowledgeable guides. Join a tour and ride through open meadows, across tranquil rivers and waterfalls, and end at the most spectacular viewpoints of Valle del Cocora.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28.jpg\" alt=\"horse riding salento colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"horse riding salento colombia\" class=\"wp-image-81918 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.