wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>As with all <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wildlife tourism<\/a>, do your research very carefully to make sure you choose a sustainable, ethical business that treats the horses with love and care. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wildlife Tourism Alternatives<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10124305\/salento-colombia-21.jpg\" alt=\"salento things to do horse riding\"><\/noscript><img width=\"255\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salento things to do horse riding\" class=\"wp-image-81861 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1448px) 100vw, 1448px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10124305\/salento-colombia-21.jpg 1448w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10124305\/salento-colombia-21-453x600.jpg 453w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10124305\/salento-colombia-21-611x810.jpg 611w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10124305\/salento-colombia-21-255x338.jpg 255w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10124305\/salento-colombia-21-23x30.jpg 23w, https: