o-bogota\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Bogota<\/a> or Medellin to Pereira or Armenia airport (around a 1-hour flight). From here, you can jump on a bus or in a taxi which will take you just under an hour. It&#x2019;s a good road, just a little bit windy at the end as you travel into the mountains and valleys of Salento.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/salento-flights\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your flight to Salento<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11090008\/salento-colombia-33.jpg\" alt=\"salento colombia night market\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salento colombia night market\" class=\"wp-image-81974 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11090008\/salento-colombia-33.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11090008\/salento-colombia-33-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11090008\/salento-colombia-33-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11090008\/salento-colombia-33-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\